{"word":"δειμαίνω","slug":"δειμαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δειμαίνω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δεῖμα'><el>δεῖμα</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to be afraid, in a fright</i>, <b>Hhymn.</b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to fear</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}